data.text:
Photo Credit: Getty Images/ Michael Kovac

Breaking News!! According to TMZ Vanessa Marcil (Genreal Hospital) and Carmine Giovinazzo are divorcing!! It seems that Vanessa Marcil (General Hospital) filed for divorce in the Los Angeles County Superior Court this week, citing “irreconcilable differences.”

Marcil is also reportedly seeking attorney’s fees and spousal support from Giovinazzo. The pair married in July 2010 and nearly a year later announced the impending birth of their first child, but Marcil suffered a miscarriage in December 2011.
